# Client (React)

## Structure
- `pages/` — route-level components (LoginPage, QueryPage, etc.)
- `components/ui/` — shadcn primitives (do not edit unless customizing)
- `components/layout/` — Sidebar, TopBar, MainLayout
- `components/query/` — SQL editor, results, schema browser
- `stores/` — Zustand (authStore, databaseStore, queryStore)
- `lib/api.ts` — all HTTP calls; add new endpoints here
- `lib/socket.ts` — Socket.io client for upload/import progress

## Patterns
```tsx
// Store usage
const { databases, fetchDatabases } = useDatabaseStore();

// API call via lib/api.ts — never raw axios in components
const result = await api.getTables(database);
```

## New page checklist
1. Component in `client/src/pages/`
2. Route in `client/src/App.tsx`
3. Nav link in `client/src/components/layout/Sidebar.tsx`
4. API fns in `client/src/lib/api.ts` if needed
5. Types in `client/src/types/`
6. Update feature spec + `docs/memory/STATE.md`

## UI
- Tailwind for layout/spacing; shadcn for interactive elements
- Match existing pages: card-based layout, sidebar navigation
- Progress events: subscribe via `lib/socket.ts` (upload/import)
